ml\" href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-includes/wlwmanifest.xml\" /><meta name=\"generator\" content=\"WordPress 5.6.17\" /><link rel='shortlink' href='https://www.kakuhan.com/' /><link rel=\"alternate\" type=\"application/json+oembed\" href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/wp-json/oembed/1.0/embed?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kakuhan.com%2F\" /><link rel=\"alternate\" type=\"text/xml+oembed\" href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/wp-json/oembed/1.0/embed?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kakuhan.com%2F&#038;format=xml\" /><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/favicon.png\" sizes=\"32x32\" /><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/favicon.png\" sizes=\"192x192\" /><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/favicon.png\" /><meta name=\"msapplication-TileImage\" content=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/favicon.png\" /></head><body class=\"page--home\"><header class=\"global-header\"><div class=\"uk-container uk-container-expand\"><nav class=\"uk-navbar-container uk-navbar-transparent\" uk-navbar><div class=\"uk-flex uk-width-expand uk-hidden@l\"><div class=\"uk-navbar-center\"><a class=\"uk-logo\" href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com\"><img src=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/kakuhan/images/common/logo.png\" alt=\"株式会社角繁のロゴ\"></a></div><div class=\"uk-navbar-right\"><a class=\"offcanvas-btn\" id=\"offcanvas-btn\" href=\"#offcanvas\" uk-toggle><span></span><span></span><span></span></a></div></div><div class=\"uk-flex uk-width-expand uk-visible@l\"><div class=\"uk-navbar-left\"><a class=\"uk-logo\" href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com\"><img src=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/kakuhan/images/common/logo.png\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div class=\"uk-navbar-right\"><ul class=\"uk-navbar-nav gnav\"><li class=\"gnav-list\"><a href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/works/\">WORKS</a></li><li class=\"gnav-list\"><a href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/about/\">ABOUT</a></li><li class=\"gnav-list\"><a href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/map/\">MAP</a></li><li class=\"gnav-list\"><a href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/recruit/\">RECRUIT</a></li><li class=\"gnav-list\"><a href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/news/\">NEWS</a></li><li class=\"gnav-list\"><a href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/gallery/\">GALLERY</a></li><li class=\"gnav-list\"><a href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/group/\">GROUP</a></li></ul></div></div></nav></div></header><main><div class=\"mv front-mv uk-background-cover\" style=\"background-image: url(https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/kakuhan/images/mv/top_2.webp);\"><div class=\"front-mv__inner\"><div class=\"block\"><img src=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/kakuhan/images/mv/catch.webp\" alt=\"\"><p class=\"text uk-text-left\">私たち株式会社 角繁は秋田杉をはじめとする<br class=\"uk-visible@m\">各種国産材や外国産材をメインに取り扱う<br class=\"uk-visible@m\">建築資材総合商社です。</p></div></div></div><section class=\"component front-news\"><div class=\"uk-container\"><div class=\"front-news__grid\"><div class=\"block\"><div class=\"component-header\"><h2 class=\"title\">NEWS<span class=\"slug\">お知らせ </span></h2></div></div><div class=\"block\"><table class=\"uk-table uk-table-responsive\"><tr><td>2026.06.02</td><td><a href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/news/\">RECRUITページの募集要項を更新しました</a></td></tr><tr><td>2026.05.21</td><td><a href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/news/\">RECRUITページの募集要項を更新しました</a></td></tr></table></div></div><div class=\"uk-text-right\"><a class=\"nav-btn\" href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/news/\">過去のお知らせ<svg class=\"arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"86.679\" height=\"57.786\" viewBox=\"0 0 86.679 57.786\"><path id=\"パス_95\" data-name=\"パス 95\" d=\"M74.732,193.263l21.883-20.21H22.329v-7.318H96.615L74.732,145.523l4.587-5.023,29.689,28.677v.432L79.319,198.286Z\" transform=\"translate(-22.329 -140.5)\" fill=\"#fff\"></path></svg></a></div></div></section><section class=\"component front-works\"><div class=\"uk-container\" id=\"uk-container\"><div class=\"component-header\"><h2 class=\"title\">WORKS<span class=\"slug\">事業内容</span></h2></div></div><div class=\"front-works__container\" id=\"front-works__container\"><div uk-slider><div class=\"uk-position-relative uk-visible-toggle uk-light\" tabindex=\"-1\"><div class=\"uk-slider-container\"><ul class=\"uk-slider-items uk-grid uk-grid-small\"><li class=\"uk-width-1-1 uk-width-auto@s\"><div class=\"uk-card uk-card-default\"><div class=\"uk-card-media-top uk-cover-container\"><canvas id=\"front_canvas\" width=\"453\" height=\"286\"></canvas><img width=\"1200\" height=\"1012\" src=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-woods_fix.jpg\" class=\"attachment-small size-small\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" uk-cover=\"uk-cover\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 453px\" srcset=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-woods_fix.jpg 1200w, https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-woods_fix-300x253.jpg 300w, https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-woods_fix-1024x864.jpg 1024w, https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-woods_fix-768x648.jpg 768w\" /></div><div class=\"uk-card-body contents\"><h3 class=\"title\">木材</h3><p class=\"contents__text\">各種国産材、外国産材を豊富に取り揃えています。建築用木材のことなら、ぜひ一度お問い合わせください。</p><div class=\"bottom\"><a href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/works/wood/\" class=\"nav-btn\">MORE<svg class=\"arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"86.679\" height=\"57.786\" viewBox=\"0 0 86.679 57.786\"><path id=\"パス_95\" data-name=\"パス 95\" d=\"M74.732,193.263l21.883-20.21H22.329v-7.318H96.615L74.732,145.523l4.587-5.023,29.689,28.677v.432L79.319,198.286Z\" transform=\"translate(-22.329 -140.5)\" fill=\"#fff\"/></svg></a></div></div></div></li><li class=\"uk-width-1-1 uk-width-auto@s\"><div class=\"uk-card uk-card-default\"><div class=\"uk-card-media-top uk-cover-container\"><canvas id=\"front_canvas\" width=\"453\" height=\"286\"></canvas><img width=\"1200\" height=\"1012\" src=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-materials.jpg\" class=\"attachment-small size-small\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" uk-cover=\"uk-cover\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 453px\" srcset=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-materials.jpg 1200w, https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-materials-300x253.jpg 300w, https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-materials-1024x864.jpg 1024w, https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-materials-768x648.jpg 768w\" /></div><div class=\"uk-card-body contents\"><h3 class=\"title\">建材・住宅設備機器</h3><p class=\"contents__text\">木材と共に建材・住宅設備機器も住宅建築の大事な材料です。木材とあわせて一括でご注文することで工期削減やビルダーの負担軽減に繋がります。最適な商品の提案も行っています。</p><div class=\"bottom\"><a href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/works/materials/\" class=\"nav-btn\">MORE<svg class=\"arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"86.679\" height=\"57.786\" viewBox=\"0 0 86.679 57.786\"><path id=\"パス_95\" data-name=\"パス 95\" d=\"M74.732,193.263l21.883-20.21H22.329v-7.318H96.615L74.732,145.523l4.587-5.023,29.689,28.677v.432L79.319,198.286Z\" transform=\"translate(-22.329 -140.5)\" fill=\"#fff\"/></svg></a></div></div></div></li><li class=\"uk-width-1-1 uk-width-auto@s\"><div class=\"uk-card uk-card-default\"><div class=\"uk-card-media-top uk-cover-container\"><canvas id=\"front_canvas\" width=\"453\" height=\"286\"></canvas><img width=\"1200\" height=\"1012\" src=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-delivery.jpg\" class=\"attachment-small size-small\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" uk-cover=\"uk-cover\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 453px\" srcset=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-delivery.jpg 1200w, https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-delivery-300x253.jpg 300w, https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-delivery-1024x864.jpg 1024w, https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-delivery-768x648.jpg 768w\" /></div><div class=\"uk-card-body contents\"><h3 class=\"title\">配送</h3><p class=\"contents__text\">小型トラックから大型トラックまで、多数準備しお客様の倉庫やご指定の建築現場まで迅速に責任を持って配送いたします。</p><div class=\"bottom\"><a href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/works/delivery/\" class=\"nav-btn\">MORE<svg class=\"arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"86.679\" height=\"57.786\" viewBox=\"0 0 86.679 57.786\"><path id=\"パス_95\" data-name=\"パス 95\" d=\"M74.732,193.263l21.883-20.21H22.329v-7.318H96.615L74.732,145.523l4.587-5.023,29.689,28.677v.432L79.319,198.286Z\" transform=\"translate(-22.329 -140.5)\" fill=\"#fff\"/></svg></a></div></div></div></li><li class=\"uk-width-1-1 uk-width-auto@s\"><div class=\"uk-card uk-card-default\"><div class=\"uk-card-media-top uk-cover-container\"><canvas id=\"front_canvas\" width=\"453\" height=\"286\"></canvas><img width=\"1200\" height=\"1012\" src=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-precut.jpg\" class=\"attachment-small size-small\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" uk-cover=\"uk-cover\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 453px\" srcset=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-precut.jpg 1200w, https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-precut-300x253.jpg 300w, https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-precut-1024x864.jpg 1024w, https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-precut-768x648.jpg 768w\" /></div><div class=\"uk-card-body contents\"><h3 class=\"title\">プレカット・CAD</h3><p class=\"contents__text\">プレカットとは工場で木材にあらかじめ加工を施し、現場の工期短縮や廃材の削減を目指す現在主流の建築スタイルです。</p><div class=\"bottom\"><a href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/works/precut/\" class=\"nav-btn\">MORE<svg class=\"arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"86.679\" height=\"57.786\" viewBox=\"0 0 86.679 57.786\"><path id=\"パス_95\" data-name=\"パス 95\" d=\"M74.732,193.263l21.883-20.21H22.329v-7.318H96.615L74.732,145.523l4.587-5.023,29.689,28.677v.432L79.319,198.286Z\" transform=\"translate(-22.329 -140.5)\" fill=\"#fff\"/></svg></a></div></div></div></li><li class=\"uk-width-1-1 uk-width-auto@s\"><div class=\"uk-card uk-card-default\"><div class=\"uk-card-media-top uk-cover-container\"><canvas id=\"front_canvas\" width=\"453\" height=\"286\"></canvas><img width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-service_1.jpg\" class=\"attachment-small size-small\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" uk-cover=\"uk-cover\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 453px\" srcset=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-service_1.jpg 1200w, https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-service_1-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-service_1-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/works-service_1-768x576.jpg 768w\" /></div><div class=\"uk-card-body contents\"><h3 class=\"title\">施工サービス</h3><p class=\"contents__text\">住宅の寿命を延ばすためには、シロアリなどから木材を守る必要があります。人やペットに安全で害虫などに高い効果を発揮するホウ酸防腐防蟻処理を行っております。</p><div class=\"bottom\"><a href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/works/service/\" class=\"nav-btn\">MORE<svg class=\"arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"86.679\" height=\"57.786\" viewBox=\"0 0 86.679 57.786\"><path id=\"パス_95\" data-name=\"パス 95\" d=\"M74.732,193.263l21.883-20.21H22.329v-7.318H96.615L74.732,145.523l4.587-5.023,29.689,28.677v.432L79.319,198.286Z\" transform=\"translate(-22.329 -140.5)\" fill=\"#fff\"/></svg></a></div></div></div></li><li class=\"uk-width-1-1 uk-width-auto@s\"><div class=\"uk-card uk-card-default\"><div class=\"uk-card-media-top uk-cover-container\"><canvas id=\"front_canvas\" width=\"453\" height=\"286\"></canvas><img width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/support_5.jpg\" class=\"attachment-small size-small\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" uk-cover=\"uk-cover\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 453px\" srcset=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/support_5.jpg 1200w, https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/support_5-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/support_5-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/support_5-768x512.jpg 768w\" /></div><div class=\"uk-card-body contents\"><h3 class=\"title\">工務店トータルサポート</h3><p class=\"contents__text\">木材・建材の販売だけでなく、プレカット・各種図面製作・各種申請代行業務・保険代理業務など、建築業務全般をサポートしております。</p><div class=\"bottom\"><a href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/works/support/\" class=\"nav-btn\">MORE<svg class=\"arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"86.679\" height=\"57.786\" viewBox=\"0 0 86.679 57.786\"><path id=\"パス_95\" data-name=\"パス 95\" d=\"M74.732,193.263l21.883-20.21H22.329v-7.318H96.615L74.732,145.523l4.587-5.023,29.689,28.677v.432L79.319,198.286Z\" transform=\"translate(-22.329 -140.5)\" fill=\"#fff\"/></svg></a></div></div></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"slider-nav uk-position-absolute uk-visible@s\" id=\"slider-nav\"><a href=\"#\" uk-slidenav-previous uk-slider-item=\"previous\"><svg class=\"arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"86.679\" height=\"57.786\" viewBox=\"0 0 86.679 57.786\"><path id=\"パス_95\" data-name=\"パス 95\" d=\"M74.732,193.263l21.883-20.21H22.329v-7.318H96.615L74.732,145.523l4.587-5.023,29.689,28.677v.432L79.319,198.286Z\" transform=\"translate(-22.329 -140.5)\" fill=\"#fff\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"#\" uk-slidenav-next uk-slider-item=\"next\"><svg class=\"arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"86.679\" height=\"57.786\" viewBox=\"0 0 86.679 57.786\"><path id=\"パス_95\" data-name=\"パス 95\" d=\"M74.732,193.263l21.883-20.21H22.329v-7.318H96.615L74.732,145.523l4.587-5.023,29.689,28.677v.432L79.319,198.286Z\" transform=\"translate(-22.329 -140.5)\" fill=\"#fff\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"front-about uk-background-norepeat front-bg-component uk-background-fixed uk-background-cover uk-position-relative uk-background-center-center\" style=\"background-image: url(https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/kakuhan/images/top/about_bg_3.webp);\"><div class=\"uk-container\"><div class=\"bg-front-block\"><div class=\"component-header bg-component-header\"><h2 class=\"title\">ABOUT<span class=\"slug\">会社案内</span></h2><p class=\"text\">私たちは木材流通においては<br>秋田県内一のシェアを誇り、<br>豊富な在庫・迅速な配達が自慢です。</p><div class=\"btn-block\"><a class=\"btn\" href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/about/\">MORE<svg class=\"arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"86.679\" height=\"57.786\" viewBox=\"0 0 86.679 57.786\"><path id=\"パス_95\" data-name=\"パス 95\" d=\"M74.732,193.263l21.883-20.21H22.329v-7.318H96.615L74.732,145.523l4.587-5.023,29.689,28.677v.432L79.319,198.286Z\" transform=\"translate(-22.329 -140.5)\" fill=\"#fff\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"front-map uk-background-norepeat front-bg-component uk-background-fixed uk-background-cover uk-position-relative uk-background-center-center\" style=\"background-image: url(https://www.kakuhan.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/kakuhan/images/top/map_bg.webp);\"><div class=\"uk-container\"><div class=\"bg-front-block right\"><div class=\"component-header bg-component-header\"><h2 class=\"title\">MAP<span class=\"slug\">事業所</span></h2><p class=\"text\">秋田市を拠点とし、<br>東北各地に事業所を<br>かまえております。</p><div class=\"btn-block\"><a class=\"btn\" href=\"https://www.kakuhan.com/map/\">MORE<svg class=\"arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"86.679\" height=\"57.786\" viewBox=\"0 0 86.679 57.786\"><path id=